    <h1>Kinder Morgan (KMI)<br/>Intrinsic Value</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A transparent, two-stage discounted cash flow valuation of Kinder Morgan, Inc. — using FY2025 actuals, disclosed assumptions, and one final number.</p>
